BlockBeats news, on September 24, DWF Labs co-founder Andrei Grachev disclosed on the social platform X that the company's synthetic stablecoin product is expected to be launched in the fourth quarter of 2024 to the first quarter of 2025, with the following features:


Expected annualized rate of return (APY): stablecoins about 12%; BTC/ETH about 15%; blue chip coins about 17%; long tail altcoins about 19%;


Full chain casting/redemption function;


A total locked value (TVL) whitelist commitment of about US$500 million has been obtained from partners and friendly institutions.

